    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Diagrams in the form of a circle divided by radii into sectors proportional to relative magnitudes, quantities, or frequencies of a set or to the number of data values in a corresponding class. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
